[?2004l[?2004h> | Category | Count | Success | Failed |
[?2004l[?2004h> |----------|-------|---------|--------|
[?2004l[?2004h> | AWS IAM | {aws_stats[0]} | {aws_stats[1]} | {aws_stats[2]} |
[?2004l[?2004h> | Database | {db_stats[0]} | {db_stats[1]} | {db_stats[2]} |
[?2004l[?2004h> | API Keys | {api_stats[0]} | {api_stats[1]} | {api_stats[2]} |
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> ## Detailed Rotation Log
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> ### AWS IAM Credentials
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> | Service | Old Key ID | New Key ID | Status | Rotated By |
[?2004l[?2004h> |---------|------------|------------|--------|------------|
[?2004l[?2004h> {generate_table_rows(aws_entries)}
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> ### Database Credentials
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> | Service | Old Key ID | New Key ID | Status | Rotated By |
[?2004l[?2004h> |---------|------------|------------|--------|------------|
[?2004l[?2004h> {generate_table_rows(db_entries)}
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> ### API Keys
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> | Service | Old Key ID | New Key ID | Status | Rotated By |
